        <!--
            To publish a release:
            1. Archive the app in Xcode (Product > Archive)
            2. Export as "Developer ID" signed app
            3. Create a .zip: ditto -c -k --keepParent WorkerWidget.app WorkerWidget-1.0.0.zip
            4. Sign the archive: ./bin/sign_update WorkerWidget-1.0.0.zip
            5. Add an <item> below with the sparkle:edSignature from step 4
            6. Upload the .zip to the GitHub Release
            7. Commit the updated appcast.xml

            Or use Sparkle's generate_appcast tool to automate steps 4-7.
        -->
    </channel>
</rss>
